234
00:13:59,641 --> 00:14:05,441
你这一夜收入总额可以超过3000美金

235
00:14:06,321 --> 00:14:08,681
你们快开工

236
00:14:09,101 --> 00:14:12,831
- 那你干嘛?
- 我要上网买鞋!

237
00:14:14,741 --> 00:14:18,231
* She'll be coming round
the mountain when she comes *

238
00:14:18,251 --> 00:14:21,771
* She'll be coming round
the mountain when she comes *

239
00:14:21,831 --> 00:14:25,181
* She'll be coming round the mountain *

